Lowry did it, right?

58:04.607 --> 58:08.111
I'm telling you this detective brother
is getting curiouser and curiouser.

58:08.194 --> 58:10.780
John's a fucking prick,
but he acts like a Boy Scout.

58:10.863 --> 58:12.699
Oh, I seen this type before.

58:12.782 --> 58:15.326
The whole family is a bunch
of self-righteous fucking do-gooders.

58:15.410 --> 58:18.371
That's bullshit. Bullshit.
They paid a girl to get rid of a kid.

58:18.454 --> 58:21.916
Come on, the whole family's
a bunch of fucking liars.

58:55.074 --> 58:59.287
After all the shit went down
at the motel, you're sure, right?

58:59.370 --> 59:03.249
The kid, Eve,
they never saw Danny up in Miami, right?

59:05.168 --> 59:09.839
All I know is Danny told me he was coming,
and then he never showed.

59:36.407 --> 59:38.493
I need to know...

59:39.410 --> 59:42.080
